NOTE ON DATA. This license covers the SOFTWARE (code) in this repository only.
It does NOT cover the abstract corpus the code assembles. The corpus is built
from third-party sources under their own terms:

  - 2007-2020 (BMC Neuroscience supplements): CC-BY, freely redistributable.
  - 2021-2025 (Journal of Computational Neuroscience supplements): free-to-read
    but NOT open-access; raw abstract text is NOT redistributed by this project.

No corpus text, PDFs, or extracted bodies are committed to this repository
(everything under data/ is gitignored). Users reconstruct the corpus locally by
running the pipeline against the original sources.
